pursuit of spirituality. In December 2011, Swamiji formed
Sruti Kendra with the main objective of reaching out to all
sections of society and to spread the sacred spiritual 
knowledge, with special focus on children and the youth, 
spreading the glory of our rich culture. He inspires the 
householders also to walk the path of dynamic karma yoga 
to identify and reach the highest goals of life.
<br/>
